quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  3,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  3,1,alif laam mem
  3,2,"Allah , woh zindah Javed hasti, jo nizaam kaayenaat ko sambhale hue hai, haqeeqat mein uss ke siwa koi khuda nahi hai"
  3,3,"uss ne tum par yeh kitaab nazil ki hai, jo haq le kar aayi hai aur unn kitabon ki tasdeeq kar rahi hai jo pehlay se aayi hui theen is se pehlay woh insanon ki hadaayat ke liye torat aur injeel nazil kar chuka hai"
  3,4,"aur is ne woh kasoti utari hai ( jo haq aur baatil ka farq daal khanay wali hai ) ab jo log Allah ke Faramin ko qubool karne se inkaar karen, un ko yaqeenan sakht saza miley gi Allah be panah taaqat ka maalik hai aur buraiee ka badla dainay wala hai"
  3,5,zameen aur aasman ki koi cheez Allah se posheeda nahi
  3,6,"wohi to hai jo tumhari maaon ke pait mein tumhari soorten, jaisi chahta hai, banata hai uss zabardast hikmat walay ke siwa koi aur khuda nahi hai"
  3,7,"wohi khuda hai, jis ne yeh kitaab tum par nazil ki hai iss kitaab mein do terhan ki ayaat hain : aik mohkmaat , jo kitaab ki asal bunyaad hain aur doosri mutashbihaat , jin logon ke dalo n mein theerh hai, woh ftne ki talaash mein hameshamutashabihaathi ke peechay parre rehtay hain aur unn ko maienay pehnanay ki koshish kya karte hain, halaank un ka haqeeqi mafhuum Allah ke siwa koi nahi jaanta ,bakhaf iss ke jo log ilm mein pukhta car hain, woh kehte hain ke"" hamara unn par imaan hai, yeh sab hamaray Rab hi ki taraf se hain"" aur sach yeh hai ke kisi cheez se sahih sabaq sirf danishmand log hi haasil karte hain"
  3,8,"woh Allah se dua karte rehtay hain ke :"" parvar-digaar! jab to hamein seedhay rasta par laga chuka hai, to phir kahin hamaray dilon ko kajji mein mubtala nah kar dejyu hamein apne khazana Faiz se rehmat ataa kar ke to hi Fayaz haqeeqi hai"
  3,9,"parvar-digaar! to yaqeenan sab logon ko aik roz jama karne wala hai, jis ke anay mein koi shuba nahi to hargiz apne waday se talnay wala nahi hai """
  3,10,"jin logon ne kufar ka rawayya ikhtiyar kya hai, inhen Allah ke muqablay mein nah unn ka maal kuch kaam day ga, nah aulaad woh dozakh ka eendhan ban kar rahen ge"
  3,11,"unn ka injaam waisa hi hoga, jaissa firaon ke sathiyon aur unn se pehlay ke na farmanoon ka ho chuka hai ke onhon ne ayaat Ellahi ko jhutlaya, nateeja yeh howa ke Allah ne un ke gunaaho par inhen pakar liya aur haq yeh hai ke Allah sakht saza dainay wala hai"
  3,12,"pas ae Muammad Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam!jin logon ne tumhari dawat ko qubool karne se inkaar kar diya hai, unn se keh do ke qareeb hai woh waqt, jab tum maghloob ho jao ge aur jahannum ki taraf hankayjao ge aur jahannum bara hi bura thikana hai"
  3,13,"tumahray liye unn do garohoon mein aik nishaan Ibrat tha, jo ( badar mein ) aik dosray se nbrd aazma hue aik giroh Allah ki raah mein lar raha tha aur dosra giroh kafir tha dekhnay walay bchshm sir dekh rahay thay ke kafir giroh momin giroh se do chand hai magar ( nateejay ne saabit kar diya ke ) Allah apni fatah o nusrat se jis ko chahta hai, madad deta hai دیدۂ Beena rakhnay walon ke liye is mein bara sabaq posheeda hai"
  3,14,"logon ke liye marghobaat-e- nafs, aurtain, olaad , sonay chandi ke dhair, cheeda ghoray, maweshi o ray zarayi zameenen barri khush aaind bana di gayi hain, magar yeh sab duniya ki chand roza zindagi ke samaan hain haqeeqat mein jo behtar thikana hai, woh to Allah ke paas hai"
  3,15,"kaho : mein tumhe batau ke un se ziyada achi cheez kya hai? jo log taqwa ki rawish ikhtiyar karen, unn ke liye un ke Rab ke pa seen baagh hain, jin ke neechay nehrein behti hon gi, wahan inhen hameshgi ki zindagi haasil hogi, pakeeza biwiyan un ki Rafeeq hon gi aur Allah ki Raza se woh Sarfraz hon ge Allah apne bundon ke ravayye par gehri nazar rakhta hai"
  3,16,"yeh woh log hain, jo kehte hain ke"" maalik! hum imaan laaye, hamari khataon se Dur guzar farma aur hamein aatish dozakh se bacha le """
  3,17,"yeh log sabr karne walay hain, rasbaazhain, farmanbardar aur Fayaz hain aur raat ki aakhri gharion mein Allah se mughfirat ki duayen manga karte hain"
  3,18,"Allah ne khud shahadat di hai ke is ke siwa koi khuda nahi hai, o ray ( yahi shahadat ) firshton aur sab ahal ilm ne bhi di hai woh insaaf par qaim hai uss zabardast hakeem ke siwa fi al waqea koi khuda nahi hai"
  3,19,"Allah ke nazdeek deen sirf islam hai is deen se hatt kar jo mukhtalif tareeqay unn logon ne ikhtiyar kiye, jinhein kitaab di gayi thi, unn ke iss tarz amal ki koi wajah is ke siwa nah thi ke unhon ne ilm aa jaane ke baad aapas mein aik dosray par zayad-ti karne ke liye aisa kya aur jo koi Allah ke ehkaam o Hadayat ki itaat se inkaar kar day, Allah ko is se hisaab letay kuch der nahi lagti hai"
  3,20,"ab agar yeh log tum se jhagra karen, tawa noon se kaho :"" mein ne aur mere pairwoo-n (maan-nay walonn )ne to Allah ke agay sir tasleem khham kar diya hai"" phir ahal kitaab aur ghair ahal kitaab dono se pucho :"" kya tum ne bhi is ki itaat o bandagi qubool ki ?"" agar ki to woh raah raast pa gay, aur agar is se mun morra to tum par sirf pegham pouncha dainay ki zimma daari thi agay Allah khud apne bundon ke mamlaat dekhnay wala hai"
  3,21,"jo log Allah ke ehkaam o Hadayat ko maan-ne se inkaar karte hain aur is ke payghambaroon ko na-haq qatal karte hain aur aisay logon ki jaan ke darpay ho jatay hain, jo Khalq khuda mein Adal o raasti ka hukum dainay ke liye utheen, un ko dard naak saza ki khush khaberi suna do"
  3,22,"yeh woh log hain jin ke aamaal duniya aur akhirat dono mein zaya hogaye, aur un ka madadgaar koi nahi hai"
  3,23,"tum ne dekha nahi jin logon ko kitaab ke ilm mein se kuch hissa mila hai, unn ka haal kya hai? unhen jab kitaab Ellahi ki taraf bulaya jata hai taakay woh unn ke darmain faisla kere, to un mein se aik fareeq is se pehlu tehi karta hai aur is faislay ki taraf anay se mun phair jata hai"
  3,24,"un ka yeh tarz amal is wajah se hai ke woh kehte hain"" aatish dozakh to hamein miss taq nah kere gi aur agar dozakh ki saza hum ko miley gi bhi to bas chand roz"" unn ke khud sakhta aqeedon ne unn ko apne deen ke muamlay mein barri ghalat fehmiyon mein daal rakha hai"
  3,25,magar kya banay gi unn par jab hum inhen uss roz jama karen ge jis ka aana yakeeni hai? is roz har shakhs ko is ki kamaai ka badla poora poora day diya jaayegaa aur kisi par zulm nah hoga
  3,26,"kaho! khudaaya! mulk ke maalik! to jisay chahay, hukoomat day aur jisay chahay, chean le jisay chahay, izzat bakhshay aur jis ko chahay, zaleel kar day bhalai tairay ikhtiyar mein hai bay shak to har cheez par Qadir hai"
  3,27,"raat ko din mein pirota howa le aata hai aur din ko raat mein jandaar mein se be jaan ko nkalta hai aur be jaan mein se jandaar ko aur jisay chahta hai, be hisaab rizaq deta hai"
  3,28,momnin ahal imaan ko chore kar kafiroon ko apna Rafeeq aur dost hargiz nah banayen jo aisa kere ga is ka Allah se koi talluq nahi haan yeh maaf hai ke tum un ke zulm se bachney ke liye bzahir aisa tarz amal ikhtiyar kar jao magar Allah tumhe apne aap se darata hai aur tumhe isi ki taraf palat kar jana hai
  3,29,"ae Nabi Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ! logon ko khabardaar kar do ke tumahray dilon mein jo kuch hai, ussay khuwa tum chupao ya zahir karo, Allah behar haal usay jaanta hai, zameen o aasman ki koi cheez is ke ilm se bahar nahi hai aur uss ka Iqtidaar har cheez par haawi hai"
  3,30,"woh din anay wala hai, jab har nafs apne kiye ka phal haazir paye ga khuwa uss ne bhalai ki ho ya buraiee is roz aadmi yeh tamanna kere ga ke kash abhi yeh din is se bohat daur hota! Allah tumhe apne aap se darata hai aur woh apne bundon ka nihayat kher khuwa hai"
  3,31,"ae Nabi Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ! logon se keh do ke,"" agar tum haqeeqat mein Allah se mohabbat rakhtay ho, to Meer y pairwi ikhtiyar karo, Allah tum se mohabbat kere ga aur tumhari khataon se dar guzar farmaiye ga woh bara maaf karne wala aur Raheem hai """
  3,32,"unn se kaho ke"" Allah aur rasool ki itaat qubool kar lau"" phir tum agar woh tumhari dawat qubool nah karen, to yaqeenan yeh mumkin nahi hai ke Allah aisay logon se mohabbat kere, jo is ki aur is ke rasool ki itaat se inkaar karte hon"
  3,33,Allah ne Aadam aur Nooh aur all ibrahim aur all Imran ko tamam duniya walon par tarjeeh day kar ( apni risalat ke liye ) muntakhib kya tha
  3,34,"yeh aik silsilay ke log thay, jo aik dosray ki nasal se peda hue thay Allah sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai"
  3,35,"( woh uss waqt sun raha tha ) jab Imran ki aurat keh rahi thi ke,"" mere parvar-digaar! mein is bachay ko jo mere pait mein hai teri Nazar karti hon, woh tairay hi kaam ke liye waqf hoga meri is peshkash ko qubool farma to suneney aur jan-nay wala hai """
  3,36,"phir jab woh bachi is ke haan peda hui to is ne kaha"" maalik! mere haan to larki peda ho gayi hai halaank jo kuch is ne jina tha, Allah ko is ki khabar thi aur larka lar ki ki terhan nahi hota kher, mein ne is ka naam maryam rakh diya hai aur mein usay aur is ki aindah nasal ko shetan mardood ke ftne se teri panah mein deti hon """
  3,37,"aakhir kaar is ke Rab ne is larki ko bakhushi qubool farma liya, ussay barri achi larki bana kar uthaya aur Zikria kuaa seen ka sarparast bana diya Zikria jab kabhi is ke paas mahaRab mein jata to is ke paas kuch nah kuch khanay peenay ka samaan paata puchta maryam! yeh tairay pa seen kahan se aaya? woh jawab deti Allah ke paas se aaya hai, Allah jisay chahta hai be hisaab deta hai"
  3,38,"yeh haal dekh kar Zikria ne apne Rab ko puraka"" parvar-digaar! apni qudrat se mujhe naik aulaad ataa kar to hi dua suneney wala hai """
  3,39,"jawab mein firshton ne aawaz di, jab ke woh mahaRab mein khara namaz parh raha tha, ke"" Allah tujhe yahya ki khush khaberi deta hai woh Allah ki taraf se aik farmaan ki tasdeeq karne o ila ban kar aeye ga is mein sardari o buzurgi ki shaan hogi kamaal darja ka Zabit hoga nabuwat se Sarfraz hoga aur صالحین mein shumaar kya jaye ga """
  3,40,"Zikria ne kaha,"" parvar-digaar! bhala mere haan larka kahan se hoga, mein to boorha ho chuka hon aur meri biwi banjh hai"" jawab mila,"" aisa hi hoga, Allah jo chahta hai karta hai """
  3,41,"arz kya"" maalik! phir koi nishani mere liye muqarrar farma day"" kaha,"" nishani yeh hai ke tum teen din taq logon se ishara ke siwa koi baat cheet nah karo ge ( ya nah krsko ge ) iss douran mein apne Rab ko bohat yaad karna aur subah o shaam is ki tasbeeh karte rehna """
  3,42,"phir woh waqt aaya jab maryam se firshton ne aakar kaha,"" ae maryam! Allah ne tujhe bargzida kya aur pakizgee ataa ki aur tamam duniya ki aurton par tujh ko tarjeeh day kar apni khidmat ke liye chunn liya"
  3,43,"ae maryam! apne Rab ki tabay farmaan ban kar reh, is ke agay sir bsjod ho, aur jo bande is ke huzoor jhuknay walay hain un ke sath to bhi jhuk ja """
  3,44,"ae Muammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ! yeh ghaib ki khabrain hain jo hum tum ko wahi ke zareya se bta rahay hain, warna tum uss waqt wahan mojood nah thay jab hekal ke khadim yeh faisla karne ke liye ke maryam ka sir parast kon ho apne apne qalam pheink rahay thay, aur nah tum uss waqt haazir thay, jab unn ke darmain jhagra barpaa tha"
  3,45,"aur jab firshton ne kaha,"" ae maryam! Allah tujhe apne aik farmaan ki khush khaberi deta hai uss ka naam maseeh ( hazrat ) Eesa Ibn maryam(alh-e-salam) hoga, duniya aur akhirat mein Muaziz hoga, Allah ke MaqarRab bundon mein shumaar kya jaye ga"
  3,46,"logon se gehware mein bhi kalaam kere ga aur barri Umar ko poanch kar bhi, aur woh aik mard Saleh hoga """
  3,47,"yeh sun kar maryam boli,"" parvar-digaar! mere haan bacha kahan se hoga, mujhe to kisi shakhs ne haath taq nahi lagaya"" jawab mila,"" aisa hi hoga, Allah jo chahta hai peda karta hai woh jab kisi kaam ke karne ka faisla farmata hai to bas kehta hai ke ho ja aur woh ho jata hai """
  3,48,"( firshton ne phir silsla-aykalaam mein kaha )"" aur Allah ussay kitaab aur hikmat ki taleem day ga, torat aur injeel ka ilm sikhayiye ga"
  3,49,"aur bani Israel ki taraf apna rasool muqarrar kere ga"" ( aur jab woh ba-hasiat rasool bani Israel ke paas aaya to is ne kaha )"" mein tumahray Rab ki taraf se tumahray paas nishani le kar aaya hon mein tumahray samnay matti se parinday ki soorat mein aik mujasma banata hon aur is mein phoonk maarta hon, woh Allah ke hukum se parindah ban jata hai mein Allah ke hukum se madar zaad andhay aur korhi ko acha karta hon aur murdy ko zindah karta hon mein tumhe batata hon ke tum kya khatay ho aur kya apne gharon mein zakheera kar ke rakhtay ho is mein tumahray liye kaafi nishani hai agar tum imaan laane walay ho"
  3,50,"aur mein uss taleem o hadaayat ki tasdeeq karne wala ban kar aaya hon jo torat mein se iss waqt mere zamana mein mojood hai aur iss liye aaya hon ke tumahray liye baaz unn cheezon ko halal kar dun jo tum par haraam kar di gayi hain dekho, mein tumahray Rab ki taraf se tumahray paas nishani le kar aaya hon, lehaza Allah se daro aur Meer y itaat karo"
  3,51,"Allah mera Rab bhi hai o ray tumhara Rab bhi, lehaza tum usi ki bandagi ikhtiyar karo, yahi seedha rasta hai """
  3,52,"jab eesa ne mehsoos kya ke bani Israel kufar o inkaar par amaada hain to is ne kaha"" kon Allah ki raah mein mera madad gaar hota hai ?"" hawarion ne jawab diya,"" hum Allah ke madadgaar hain, hum Allah par imaan laaye, gawah raho ke hum muslim ( Allah ke agay sir itaat jhuka dainay walay ) hain"
  3,53,"maalik! jo farmaan to ne nazil kya hai hum ne usay maan liya aur rasool ki pairwi qubool ki, hamara naam gawahi dainay walon mein likh le """
  3,54,phir bani Israel ( maseeh ke khilaaf ) khufia tadbeerye karne lagey jawab mein Allah ne bhi apni khufia tadbeer ki aur aisi tdbiron mein Allah sab se barh kar hai
  3,55,"( woh Allah ki khufia tadbeer hi thi ) jab uss ne kaha ke,"" ae eesa! ab mein tujhe wapas le lon ga aur tujh ko apni taraf utha lon ga aur jinhon ne tera inkaar kya hai unn se ( yani un ki mayt se aur un ke ganday mahol mein un ke sath rehne se ) tujhe pak kar dun ga aur teri pairwi karne walon ko qayamat taq un logon par baladst rakhon ga jinhon ne tera inkaar kya hai phir tum sab ko aakhir mere paas aana hai, uss waqt mein unn baton ka faisla kar dun ga jin mein tumahray darmain ikhtilaaf howa hai"
  3,56,jin logon ne kufar o inkaar ki rawish ikhtiyar ki hai inhen duniya aur akhirat dono mein sakht saza dun ga aur woh koi madadgaar nah payen ge
  3,57,"aur jinhon ne imaan aur naik amli ka rawayya ikhtiyar kya hai inhen unn ke ajar poooray poooray day diye jayen ge aur khoob jaan le ke zaalmon se Allah hargiz mohabbat nahi karta """
  3,58,yeh ayaat aur hikmat se labraiz tazkeray hain jo hum tumhe suna rahay hain
  3,59,Allah ke nazdeek eesa ki misaal Aadam ki si hai ke Allah ne usay matti se peda kya aur hukum diya ke ho ja aur woh ho gaya
  3,60,yeh asal haqeeqat hai jo tumahray Rab ki taraf se batayi ja rahi hai aur tum un logon mein shaamil nah ho jo is mein shak karte hain
  3,61,"yeh ilm aa jaane ke baad ab koi is maamla mein tum se jhagra kere to ae MuhammadSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam ! is se kaho,"" aao hum aur tum khud bhi aa jayen aur apne apne baal bachon ko bhi le ayen aur Kkhuda se dua karen ke jo jhoota ho uss par khuda ki laanat ho """
  3,62,"yeh bilkul sahih waqeat hain, aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah ke siwa koi khudawand nahi hai, aur woh Allah hi ki hasti hai jis ki taaqat sab se baala aur jis ki hikmat nizaam aalam mein car farma hai"
  3,63,pas agar yeh log ( iss shart par muqaabla mein anay se ) mun morhin to ( unn ka mufsid hona saaf khil jaye ga ) aur Allah to mfsdon ke haal se waaqif hi hai
  3,64,"kaho,"" ae ahal kitaab! aao aik aisi baat ki taraf jo hamaray aur tumahray darmain yaksaa hai yeh ke hum Allah ke siwa kisi ki bandagi nah karen, is ke sath kisi ko shareek nah tehra-ayn aur hum mein se koi Allah ke siwa kisi ko apna Rab nah bana le"" is dawat ko qubool karne se agar woh mun morhin to saaf keh do ke gawah raho, hum to muslim ( sirf khuda ki bandagi o itaat karne walay ) hain"
  3,65,ae ahal kitaab! tum ibrahim ke baray mein hum se kyun jhagra karte ho? torat aur injeel to ibrahim ke baad hi nazil hui hain phir kya tum itni baat bhi nahi samajte
  3,66,"tum log jin cheezon ka ilm rakhtay ho unn mein to khoob bhsin kar chuke, ab un mamlaat mein kyun behas karne chalay ho jin ka tumahray paas kuch bhi ilm nahi Allah jaanta hai, tum nahi jantay"
  3,67,"ibrahim nah yahodi tha nah isaai, balkay woh aik muslim yaksu tha aur woh hargiz mushrikon mein se nah tha"
  3,68,ibrahim se nisbat rakhnay ka sab se ziyada haq agar kisi ko pohanchana hai to unn logon ko pohanchana hai jinhon ne is ki pairwi ki aur ab yeh nabi aur is ke maan-ne walay iss nisbat ke ziyada haq daar hain Allah sirf aُnhi ka haami o madadgaar hai jo imaan rakhtay hon
  3,69,"( ae imaan laane walo ) ahal kitaab mein se aik giroh chahta hai ke kisi terhan tumhe raah raast se hata day, halaank Dur haqeeqat woh apne siwa kisi kogumrahi mein nahi daal rahay hain magar inhen is ka shaoor nahi hai"
  3,70,ae ahal kitaab! kyun Allah ki ayaat ka inkaar karte ho halaank tum khud un ka mushahida kar rahay ho ?
  3,71,ae ahal kitaab! kyun haq ko baatil ka rang charha kar mushtaba banatay ho? kyun jantay bojhtayhaq ko chupatay ho ?
  3,72,"ahal kitaab mein se aik giroh kehta hai ke is nabi ke maan-ne walon par jo kuch nazil howa hai is par subah imaan lao aur shaam ko is se inkaar kar do, shayad is tarkeeb se yeh log apne imaan se phir jayen"
  3,73,"neez yeh log aapas mein kehte hain ke apne mazhab walay ke siwa kisi ki baat nah manu ae Nabi ! un se keh do ke,"" asal mein hadaayat to Allah ki hadaayat hai aur yeh usi ki deen hai ke kisi ko wohi kuch day diya jaye jo kabhi tum ko diya gaya tha, ya yeh ke dosaron ko tumahray Rab ke huzoor paish karne ke liye tumahray khilaaf quwwat Hujjat mil jaye"" ae Nabi ! un se kaho ke,"" fazl o Sharf Allah ke ikhtiyar mein hai, jisay chahay ataa farmaiye woh wasee al nazr hai aur sab kuch jaanta hai"
  3,74,"apni rehmat ke liye jis ko chahta hai makhsoos kar laita hai aur is ka fazl bohat bara hai """
  3,75,"ahal kitaab mein koi to aisa hai ke agar tum is ke aetmaad par maal o doulat ka aik dhair bhi day do to woh tumhara maal tumhe ada kar day ga, aur kisi ka haal yeh hai ke agar tum aik dinar ke maamla mein bhi is par bharosa karo to woh ada nah kere ga ila yeh ke tum is ke sir par sawaar ho jao unn ki is ikhlaqi haalat ka sabab yeh hai ke woh kehte hain,"" ummyu-N ( ghair yahodi logon ) ke maamla mein hum par koi muwakhza nahi hai"" aur yeh baat woh mehez jhoot ghurr kar Allah ki taraf mansoob karte hain, halaank inhen maloom hai ke Allah ne aisi koi baat nahi farmai hai aakhir kyun unn se baz purse nah hogi ?"
  3,76,"jo bhi apne ehad ko poora kere ga aur buraiee se bach kar rahay ga woh Allah ka mehboob banay ga, kyunkay parhaiz gaar log Allah ko pasand hain"
  3,77,"rahay woh log jo Allah ke ehad aur apni qasmon ko thori qeemat par beech daaltay hain, to un ke liye akhirat mein koi hissa nahi, Allah qayamat ke roz nah unn se baat kere ga nah unn ki taraf dekhe ga aur nah inhen pak kere ga, balkay unn ke liye to sakht dard naak saza hai"
  3,78,"unn mein kuch log aisay hain jo kitaab parhte hue is terhan zabaan ka ulat phair karte hain ke tum samjhoo jo kuch woh parh rahay hain woh kitaab hi ki ibaarat hai, halaank woh kitaab ki ibaarat nahi hoti, woh kehte hain ke yeh jo kuch hum parh rahay hain yeh khuda ki taraf se hai, halaank woh khuda ki taraf se nahi hota, woh jaan boojh kar jhoot baat Allah ki taraf mansoob kar dete hain"
  3,79,kisi ensaan ka yeh kaam nahi hai ke Allah to is ko kitaab aur hukum aur nabuwat ataa farmaiye aur woh logon se kahe ke Allah ke bajaye tum mere bande ban jao woh to yahi kahe ga ke sachey Rabbani bano jaissa ke is kitaab ki taleem ka taqaza hai jisay tum parhte aur parhatay ho
  3,80,woh tum se hargiz yeh nah kahe ga ke firshton ko ya payghambaroon ko apna Rab bana lau kya yeh mumkin hai ke aik nabi tumhe kufar ka hukum day jab ke tum muslim ho ?
  3,81,"yaad karo, Allah ne payghambaroon se ehad liya tha ke,"" aaj hum ne tumhe kitaab aur hikmat o Danish se nawaza hai, kal agar koi dosra rasool tumahray paas usi taleem ki tasdeeq karta howa aeye jo pehlay se tumahray paas mojood hai, to tum ko is par imaan lana hoga aur is ki madad karni hogi"" yeh irshad farma kar Allah ne poocha,"" kya tum iss ka iqraar karte ho aur is par meri taraf se ehad ki bhaari zimma daari uthatay ho ?"" onhon ne kaha haan hum iqraar karte hain Allah ne farmaya,"" acha to gawah raho aur mein bhi tumahray sath gawah hon"
  3,82,"is ke baad jo apne ehad se phir jaye wohi fasik hai """
  3,83,ab kya yeh log Allah ki itaat ka tareeqa ( deen Allah ) chore kar koi aur tareeqa chahtay hain? halaank aasman o zameen ki saari cheeze chaar o na chaar Allah hi ki tabay farmaan ( muslim ) hain aur usi ki taraf sab ko palatna hai ?
  3,84,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! kaho ke"" hum Allah ko mantay hain, uss taleem ko mantay hain jo hum par nazil ki gayi hai, unn talemaat ko bhi mantay hain jo ibrahim, Ismael, ishaq, yaqoob aur aulaad yaqoob par nazil hui theen aur unn Hadayat par bhi imaan rakhtay hain jo( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)aur eesa aur dosray payghambaroon ko unn ke Rab ki taraf se di gayeen hum un ke darmain farq nahi karte aur hum Allah ke tabay farmaan ( muslim ) hain """
  3,85,is farmaa bardari ( islam ) ke siwa jo shakhs koi aur tareeqa ikhtiyar karna chahay is ka woh tareeqa hargiz qubool nah kya jaye ga aur akhirat mein woh nakaam o namuraad rahay ga
  3,86,kaisay ho sakta hai ke Allah unn logon ko hadaayat bakhshay jinhon ne Nemat imaan pa lainay ke baad phir kufar ikhtiyar kya halaank woh khud is baat par gawahi day chuke hain ke yeh rasool haq par hai aur un ke paas roshan nishanain bhi aa chuki hain Allah zaalmon ko to hadaayat nahi diya karta
  3,87,un ke zulm ka sahih badla yahi hai ke un par Allah aur firshton aur tamam insanon ki phatkaar hai
  3,88,"isi haalat mein woh hamesha rahen ge, nah un ki saza mein takhfeef hogi aur nah inhen mohlat di jaye gi"
  3,89,"Albata woh log bach jayen ge jo iss ke baad tauba kar ke apne tarz amal ki islaah kar len, Allah bakhsnay wala aur reham frmane wala hai"
  3,90,"magar jin logon ne imaan laane ke baad kufar ikhtiyar kya, phir apne kufar mein barhatay chalay gay un ki tauba bhi qubool nah hogi, aisay log to pakkay gumraah hain"
  3,91,"yaqeen rakho, jin logon ne kufar ikhtiyar kya aur kufar hi ki haalat mein jaan di unn mein se koi agar apne aap ko saza se bachanay ke liye roye zameen bhar kar bhi sona Fidya mein day to ussay qubool nah kya jaye ga aisay logon ke liye dard naak saza tayyar hai aur o hay apna koi madadgaar nah payen ge"
  3,92,"tum neki ko nahi poanch satke jab taq ke apni woh cheeze ( khuda ki raah mein ) kharch nah karo jinhein tum Aziz rakhtay ho, aur jo kuch tum kharch karo ge Allah is se be khabar nah hoga"
  3,93,"khanay ki yeh saari cheeze ( jo Shariat Muhammad iSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam mein halal hain ) bani Israel ke liye bhi halal theen, Albata baaz cheeze aisi theen jinhein Touraat ke nazil kiye jaane se pehlay Israel ne khud apne oopar haraam kar liya tha un se kaho, agar tum ( a pannay aitraaz mein ) sachey ho to lao Touraat aur paish karo is ki koi ibaarat"
  3,94,is ke baad bhjo log apni jhooti gharri hui baatein Allah ki taraf mansoob karte rahen o hi Dur haqeeqat zalim hain
  3,95,"kaho, Allah ne jo kuch farmaya hai sach farmaya hai, tum ko yaksu ho kar ibrahim ke tareeqa ki pairwi karni chahiye, aur ibrahim shirk karne walon mein se nah tha"
  3,96,be shak sab se pehli ibadat gaah jo insanon ke liye taamer hui woh wohi hai jo mecca mein waqay hai is ko kher o barket di gayi thi aur tamam Jahan walon ke liye markaz hadaayat banaya gaya tha
  3,97,"is mein khuli hui nishanain hain, ibrahim ka maqam ibadat hai, aur iss ka haal yeh hai ke jo iss mein daakhil howa Mamoon ho gaya logon par Allah ka yeh haq hai ke jo is ghar taq pounchanay ki istetat rakhta ho woh is ka hajj kere, aur jo koi is hukum ki pairwi se inkaar kere to usay maloom ho jana chahiye ke Allah tamam daal naya walon se be niaz hai"
  3,98,"kaho, ae ahal kitaab! tum kyun Allah ki baatein maan-ne se inkaar karte ho? jo harkatein tum kar rahay ho Allah sab kuch dekh raha hai"
  3,99,"kaho, ae ahal kitaab! yeh tumhari kya rawish hai ke jo Allah ki baat maanta hai ussay bhi tum Allah ke rasta se roktay ho aur chahtay ho ke woh tedhi raah chalay, halaank tum khud ( is ke raah raast honay par ) gawah ho tumhari harkato se Allah ghaafil nahi hai"
  3,100,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, agar tum ne inn ahal kitaab mein se aik giroh ki baat maani to yeh tumhe imaan se phir kufar ki taraf phair le jayen ge"
  3,101,tumahray liye kufar ki taraf jaane ka ab kya mauqa baqi hai jab ke tum ko Allah ki ayaat sunai ja rahi hain aur tumahray darmain is kaRasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam mojood hai? jo Allah ka daman mazbooti ke sath thaamay ga woh zaroor raah raast paley ga
  3,102,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, Allah se daro jaissa ke is se darny ka haq hai tum ko mout nah aeye magar is haal mein ke tum muslim ho"
  3,103,"sab mil kar Allah ki rassi ko mazboot pakar lau aur tafarruqa mein nah parro Allah ke uss ahsaan ko yaad rakho jo is ne tum par kya hai tum aik dosray ke dushman thay, uss ne tumahray dil joor diye aur is ke fazl o karam se tum bhai bhai ban gay tum aag se bharay hue aik garhay ke kinare kharray thay, Allah ne tum ko is se bacha liya is terhan Allah apni nishanain tumahray samnay roshan karta hai shayad ke inn alamton se tumhe apni Falah ka seedha rasta nazar aa jaye"
  3,104,"tum mein kuch log to aisay zaroor hi rehne chahaiyn jo neki ki taraf bulayen, bhalai ka hukum den, aur buraiyon se roktay rahen jo log yeh kaam karen ge wohi Falah payen ge"
  3,105,kahin tum unn logon ki terhan nah ho jana jo firqoun mein Butt gay aur khuli khuli wazeh Hadayat panay ke baad phir ikhtilafat mein mubtala hue jinhon ne yeh rawish ikhtiyar ki woh uss roz sakhtsaza payen ge
  3,106,"jabkay kuch log surkh ro hon ge aur kuch logon ka mun kala hoga, jin ka mun kala hoga ( un se kaha jaye ga ke ) Nemat imaan panay ke baad bhi tum ne kafirana rawayya ikhtiyar kya? acha to ab iss kufran Nemat ke sila mein azaab ka maza chako"
  3,107,rahay woh log jin ke chehray roshan hon ge to unn ko Allah ke daman rehmat mein jagah miley gi aur hamesha woh isi haalat mein rahen ge
  3,108,yeh Allah ke arshadat hain jo hum tumhe theek theek snarhe hain kyunkay Allah duniya walon par zulm karne ka koi iradah nahi rakhta
  3,109,zameen o aasman ki saari cheezon ka maalik Allah hai aur saaray mamlaat Allah hi ke huzoor paish hotay hain
  3,110,"ab duniya mein woh behtareen giroh tum ho jisay insanon ki hadaayat o islaah ke liye maidan mein laya gaya hai tum neki ka hukum dete ho, badi se roktay ho aur Allah par imaan rakhtay ho yeh ahal kitaab imaan laatay to unhi ke haq mein behtar tha agarchay un mein kuch log imaan daar bhi paye jatay hain magar inn ke beshtar afraad nafarman hain"
  3,111,"yeh tumhara kuch bigaar nahi satke, ziyada se ziyada bas kuch saata satke hain agar yeh tum se lrhin ge to muqaabla mein peeth deikhein ge, phir aisay be bas hon ge ke kahin se inn ko madad nah miley gi"
  3,112,"yeh jahan bhi paye gay inn par zillat ki maar hi pari, kahin Allah ke zimma ya insanon ke zimma mein panah mil gayi to yeh aur baat hai yeh Allah ke ghazab mein ghar chuke hain, un par mohtaji omaghloobimusallat kar di gayi hai, aur yeh sab kuch sirf is wajah se howa hai ke yeh Allah ki ayaat se kufar karte rahay aur unhon ne payghambaroon ko na-haq qatal kya yeh un ki nafarmanio-n aur zayadtio ka injaam hai"
  3,113,"magar saaray ahal kitaab yaksaa nahi hain un mein kuch log aisay bhi hain jo raah raast par qaim hain, raton ko Allah ki ayaat parhte hain aur uskay agay sajda raiz hotay hain"
  3,114,"Allah aur roz akhirat par imaan rakhtay hain, neki ka hukum dete hain, buraiyon se roktay hain aur bhalai ke kamon mein sargaram rehtay hain yeh Saleh log hain"
  3,115,"aur jo neki bhi yeh karen ge is ki na qadri nah ki jaye gi, Allah parhaizgaar logon ko khoob jaanta hai"
  3,116,"rahay woh log jinhon ne kufar ka rawayya ikhtiyar kya to Allah ke muqaabla mein un ko nah un ka maal kuch kaam day ga nah aulaad, woh to aag mein jaane walay log hain aur aag hi mein hamesha rahen ge"
  3,117,jo kuch woh apni is duniya ki zindagi mein kharch kar rahay hain uss ki misaal uss howa ki si hai jis mein paala ho aur woh unn logon ki khaiti par chalay jinhon ne apne oopar zulm kya hai aur usay barbaad kar ke rakh day Allah ne un par zulm nahi kya Dur haqeeqat yeh khud apne oopar zulm kar rahay hain
  3,118,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, apni jamaat ke logon ke siwa dosaron ko apna raaz daar nah banaao woh tumhari kharabi ke kisi mauqa se faida uthany mein nahi chokte tumhe jis cheez se nuqsaan puhanche wohi un ko mehboob hai un ke dil ka bughz un ke mun se nikla parta hai aur jo kuch woh apne seenon mein chupaye hue hain woh is se shadeed tar hai hum ne tumhe saaf saaf Hadayat day di hain, agar tum aqal rakhtay ho ( to un se talluq rakhnay mein ahthyat bartu ge )"
  3,119,"tum un se mohabbat rakhtay ho magar woh tum se mohabbat nahi rakhtay halaank tum tamam kutub aasmani ko mantay ho jab woh tum se mlitay hain to kehte hain ke hum ne bhi ( tumahray rasool aur tumhari kitaab ko ) maan liya hai, magar jab judda hotay hain to tumahray khilaaf un ke ghaiz o ghazab ka yeh haal hota hai ke apni ungelian chabanay lagtay hain un se keh do ke apne gussa mein aap jal mrw Allah dilon ke chupay hue raaz taq jaanta hai"
  3,120,"tumhara bhala hota hai to un ko bura maloom hota hai, aur tum par koi museebat aati hai to yeh khush hotay hain magar un ki koi tadbeer tumahray khilaaf kargar nahi hosakti bashart e kay tum sabr se kaam lau aur Allah se dar kar kaam karte raho jo kuch yeh kar rahay hain Allah uss par haawi hai"
  3,121,( aePeghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam musalmanoon ke samnay uss mauqa ka zikar karo ) jab tum subah saweray apne ghar se niklay thay aur ( ahad ke maidan mein ) musalmanoon ko jung ke liye ja baja mamoor kar rahay thay Allah saari baatein santa hai aur woh nihayat bakhabar hai
  3,122,"yaad karo jab tum mein se do giroh buzdali daal khanay par amaada hogaye thay, halaank Allah un ki madad par mojood tha aur mominoun ko Allah hi par bharosa rakhna chahiye"
  3,123,"aakhir is se pehlay jung badar mein Allah tumhari madad kar chuka tha halaank is waqt tum bohat kamzor thay lehaza tum ko chahiye ke Allah ki na shukar y se bachcho, umeed hai ke ab tum shukar guzaar bano ge"
  3,124,"yaad karo jab tum mominoun se keh rahay thay,"" kya tumahray liye yeh baat kaafi nahi ke Allah teen hazaar farishtay utaar kar tumhari madad kere? """
  3,125,"be shak, agar tum sabr karo aur khuda se drtay hue kaam karo to jis aan dushman tumahray oopar charh kar ayen ge usi aan tumhara rab ( teen hazaar nahi ) paanch hazaar sahib nishaan firshton se tumhari madad kere ga"
  3,126,yeh baat Allah ne tumhe is liye bta di hai ke tum khush ho jao aur tumahray dil mutmaen ho jayen fatah o nusrat jo kuch bhi hai Allah ki taraf se hai jo barri qowat wala aur Dana o Beena hai
  3,127,"( aur yeh madad woh tumhe is liye day ga ) taakay kufar ki raah chalne walon ka aik baazu kaat day, ya un ko aisi zaleel shikast day ke woh naa-muraadi ke sath paspaa ho jayen"
  3,128,"(ae Peghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam) faisla ke ikhtiyarat mein tumhara koi hissa nahi, Allah ko ikhtiyar hai chahay inhen maaf kere, chahay saza day kyunkay woh zalim hain"
  3,129,"zameen aur asmano mein jo kuch hai is ka maalik Allah hai, jis ko chahay bakhash day aur jis ko chahay azaab day, o hay maaf karne wala aur Raheem hai"
  3,130,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, yeh barhta aur charhata sood khana chore do aur Allah se daro, umeed hai ke Falah pao ge"
  3,131,uss aag se bachcho jo kafiroon ke liye muhayya ki gayi hai
  3,132,"aur Allah aur rasool ka hukum maan lau, tawaqqa hai ke tum par reham kya jaye ga"
  3,133,"daud kar chalo aُ seen raah par jo tumahray rab ki bakhshish aur uss jannat ki taraf jati hai jis ki wusat zameen aur asmano jaisi hai, aur woh unn khuda taras logon ke liye muhayya ki gayi"
  3,134,"jo har haal mein apne maal kharch karte hain khuwa bad haal hon ya khush haal, jo ghusse ko pi jatay hain aur dosaron ke qasoor maaf kar dete hain aisay naik log Allah ko bohat pasand hain"
  3,135,aur jin ka haal yeh hai ke agar kabhi koi fehash kaam un se sarzad ho jata hai ya kisi gunah ka irtikaab kar ke woh apne oopar zulm kar baithtay hain to maan Allah inhen yaad aa jata hai aur is se woh apneKasoroo-n ki maffi chahtay hain kyunkay Allah ke siwa aur kon hai jo gunah maaf karsaktha ho o ray woh deedaa o danista apne kiye par israar nahi karte
  3,136,aisay logon ki jaza un ke rab ke paas yeh hai ke woh un ko maaf kar day ga aur aisay baghoon mein inhen daakhil kere ga jin ke neechay nhrin behti hongi aur wahan woh hamesha rahen ge kaisa acha badla hai naik amal karne walon ke liye
  3,137,"tum se pehlay bohat se daur guzar chuke hain, zameen mein chal phir kar dekh lau ke unn logon ka kya injaam howa jinhon ne ( Allah ke ehkaam o Hadayat ko ) jhtlaya"
  3,138,yeh logon ke liye aik saaf aur Sarih tanbeeh hai aur jo Allah se drtay hon unn ke liye hadaayat aur nasiyaat
  3,139,"dil shakista nah ho, gham nah karo, tum hi ghalib raho ge agar tum momin ho"
  3,140,"a seen waqt agar tumhen chout lagi hai to is se pehlay aisi hi chout tumahray mukhalif fareeq ko bhi lag chuki hai yeh to zamana ke nasheeb o faraz hain jinhein hum logon ke darmain gardish dete rehtay hain tum par yeh waqt a seen liye laya gaya ke Allah dekhna chahta tha ke tum mein sachey momin kon hain, aur un logon ko chhant lena chahta tha jo waqai ( raasti ke ) gawah hon kyunkay zalim log Allah ko pasand nahi hain"
  3,141,aur woh is azmaish ke zareya se mominoun ko allag chhant kar kafiroon ki srkobi kar dena chahta tha
  3,142,kya tum ne yeh samajh rakha hai ke yuhin jannat mein chalay jao ge halaank abhi Allah ne yeh to dekha hi nahi ke tum mein kon woh log hain jo is ki raah mein jaanen lrhane walay aur is ki khatir sabr karne walay hain
  3,143,"tum to mout ki tamannaye kar rahay thay! magar yeh uss waqt ki baat thi jab mout samnay nah aayi thi, lau ab woh tumahray samnay aa gayi aur tum ne ussay aankhon dekh liya"
  3,144,"Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallamis ke siwa kuch nahi ke bas aik rasool hain, unn se pehlay aur rasool bhi guzar chuke hain, phir kya agar woh mar jayen ya qatal kar diye jayen to tum log ultay paon phir jao ge? yaad rakho! jo ulta phiray ga woh Allah ka kuch nuqsaan nah kere ga, Albata jo Allah ke shukar guzaar bande ban kar rahen ge inhen woh is ki jaza day ga"
  3,145,"koi Zee rooh Allah ke azan ke baghair nahi mar sakta . mout ka waqt to likha howa hai jo shakhs sawab duniya ke iradah se kaam kere ga is ko hum duniya hi mein se den ge, aur jo sawab akhirat ke iradah se kaam kere ga woh akhirat ka sawab paye ga aur shukar karne walon ko hum unn ki jaza zaroor ataa karen ge"
  3,146,"iss se pehlay kitney hi nabi aisay guzar chuke hain jin ke sath mil kar bohat se khuda paraston ne jung ki Allah ki raah mein jo museebatein unn par parrin un se woh dil shakista nahi hue, unhon ne kamzoree nahi dikhayi, woh ( baatil ke agay ) surangoon nahi hue aisay hi sabroo-n ko Allah pasand karta hai"
  3,147,"un ki dua bas yeh thi ke,"" ae hamaray rab! hamari ghaltion aur kotahyon se dar guzar farma, hamaray kaam mein tairay hudood se jo kuch tajawaz ho gaya ho ussay maaf kar day, hamaray qadam jama day aur kafiroon ke muqaabla mein hamari madad kar """
  3,148,aakhir kaar Allah ne un ko duniya ka sawab bhi diya aur is se behtar sawab akhirat bhi ataa kya Allah ko aisay hi naik amal log pasand hain
  3,149,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, agar tum unn logon ke ishaaron par chalo ge jinhon ne kufar ki raah ikhtiyar ki hai to woh tum ko ulta phair le jayen ge aur tum namuraad ho jao ge"
  3,150,( unn ki baatein ghalat hain ) haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah tumhara haami o madadgaar hai aur woh behtareen madad karne wala hai
  3,151,"anqareeb woh waqt anay wala hai jab hum munkareen haq ke dilon mein roab bitha den ge, is liye ke onhon ne Allah ke sath unn ko khudai mein shareek ٹ Tehraya hai jin ke shareek honay par Allah ne koi sanad nazil nahi ki unn ka aakhri thikana jahannum hai aur bohat hi buri hai woh qiyam gaah jo unn zaalmon ko naseeb hogi"
  3,152,"Allah ne ( taied o nusrat ka ) jo wada tum se kya tha woh to uss ne poora kar diya ibtida mein uss ke hukum se tum hi unn ko qatal kar rahay thay magar jab tum ne kamzoree dikhayi aur apne kaam mein baahum ikhtilaaf kya, aur jounhi ke woh cheez Allah ne tumhe dikhayi jis ki mohabbat mein tum girftar thay ( yani maal ghanemat ) tum apne sardar ke hukum ki khilaaf warzi kar baithy is liye ke tum mein se kuch log duniya ke taalib thay aur kuch akhirat ki khwahish rakhtay thay tab Allah ne tumhe kafiroon ke muqaabla mein paspaa kar diya taakay tumhari azmaish kere aur haq yeh hai ke Allah ne phir bhi tumhe maaf hi kar diya kyunkay mominoun par Allah barri nazar inayat rakhta hai"
  3,153,"yaad karo jab tum bhage chalay ja rahay thay, kisi ki taraf palat kar dekhnay taq ka hosh tumhe nah tha, aur Rasool Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam tumahray peechay tum ko pukaar raha tha uss waqt tumhari is rawish ka badla Allah ne tumhe yeh diya ke tum ko ranj par ranj diye taakay aindah ke liye tumhe yeh sabaq miley ke jo kuch tumahray haath se jaye ya jo museebat tum par nazil ho is par malool nah ho Allah tumahray sab aamaal se bakhabar hai"
  3,154,"is gham ke baad phir Allah ne tum mein se kuch logon par aisi itminan ki si haalat taari kar di ke woh avnghne lagey magar aik dosra giroh, jis ke liye saari ahmiyat bas apne mafaad hi ki thi, Allah ke mutaliq terhan terhan ke jahilana gumaan karne laga jo sara sar khilaaf haq thay yeh log ab kehte hain ke,"" is kaam ke chalanay mein hamara bhi koi hissa hai ?"" un se kaho"" ( kisi ka koi hissa nahi ) iss kaam ke saaray ikhtiyarat Allah ke haath mein hain"" darasal yeh log apne dilon mein jo baat chupaye hue hain ussay tum par zahir nahi karte un ka asal matlab yeh hai ke,"" agar ( qayadat ke ) ikhtiyarat mein hamara kuch hissa hota to yahan hum nah maaray jatay"" un se keh do ke,"" agar tum apne gharon mein bhi hotay to jin logon ki mout likhi hui thi woh khud apni qatal gaahon ki taraf nikal atay"" aur yeh maamla jo paish aaya, yeh to is liye tha ke jo kuch tumahray seenon mein posheeda hai Allah ussay aazma le aur jo khout tumahray dilon mein hai ussay chhant day, Allah dilon ka haal khoob jaanta hai"
  3,155,"tum mein se jo log muqaabla ke din peeth phair gay thay unn ki a seen laghzish ka sabab yeh tha ke un ki baaz kamzoriyon ki wajah se shetan ne unn ke qadam dagmaga diye thay Allah ne inhen maaf kar diya, Allah bohat dar guzar karne wala aur Burdbar hai"
  3,156,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, kafiroon ki si baatein nah karo jin ke Aziz o Iqareb agar kabhi safar par jatay hain ya jung mein shareek hotay hain ( aur wahan kisi haadsa se do chaar ho jatay hain ) to woh kehte hain ke agar woh hamaray paas hotay to nah maaray jatay aur nah qatal hotay Allah is qisam ki baton ko un ke dilon mein hasrat o andoh ka sabab bana deta hai, warna darasal maarny aur jalanay wala to Allah hi hai aur tumhari harkaat par wohi nigaran hai"
  3,157,agar tum Allah ki raah mein maaray jao ya mar jao to Allah ki jo rehmat aur bakhshish tumahray hissa mein aeye gi woh unn saari cheezon se ziyada behtar hai jinhein yeh log jama karte hain
  3,158,aur khuwa tum mrw ya maaray jao bahar haal tum sab ko simat kar jana Allah hi ki taraf hai
  3,159,"(ae Peghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam) yeh Allah ki barri rehmat hai ke tum inn logon ke liye bohat naram mizaaj waqay hue ho warna agar kahin tum tund khoo aur sang dil hotay to yeh sab tumahray gardo paish se chaatt jatay inn ke qasoor maaf kar do, inn ke haq mein dua ye mughfirat karo, aur deen ke kaam mein un ko bhi shareek mahswara rakho, phir jab tumhara azm kisi raye par mustahkam ho jaye to Allah par bharosa karo, Allah ko woh log pasand hain jo usi ke bharoosay par kaam karte hain"
  3,160,"Allah tumhari madad par ho to koi taaqat tum par ghalib anay wali nahi, aur woh tumhe chore day, to is ke baad kon hai jo tumhari madad karsaktha ho? pas jo sachey momin hain un ko Allah hi par bharosa rakhna chahiye"
  3,161,"kisi nabi ka yeh kaam nahi ho sakta ke woh khayanat kar jaye aur jo koi khayanat kere to woh apni khayanat sameit qayamat ke roz haazir ho jaye ga, phir har mutnaqas ko is ki kamaai ka poora poora badla mil jaye ga aur kisi par kuch zulm nah hoga"
  3,162,bhala yeh kaisay ho sakta hai ke jo shakhs hamesha Allah ki Raza par chalne wala ho woh uss shakhs ke se kaam kere jo Allah ke ghazab mein ghar gaya ho aur jis ka aakhri thikana jahannum ho jo bad tareen thikana hai ?
  3,163,Allah ke nazdeek dono qisam ke admio-n mein badarjahafarq hai aur Allah sab ke aamaal par nazar rakhta hai
  3,164,"dar haqeeqat ahal imaan par to Allah ne yeh bohat bara ahsaan kya hai ke unn ke darmain khud unhi mein se aik aisa paighambar uthaya jo is ki ayaat inhen sunataa hai, unn ki zindagion ko sanwarta hai aur unn ko kitaab aur danai ki taleem deta hai, halaank is se pehlay yahi log Sarih gmrahyon mein parre hue thay"
  3,165,"aur yeh tumhara kya haal hai ke jab tum par museebat aa pari to tum kehnay lagey yeh kahan se aayi? halaank ( jung badar mein ) is se daal o gani museebat tumahray hathon ( fareeq mukhalif par ) par chuki hai ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! inn se kaho, yeh museebat tumhari apni layi hui hai, Allah har cheez par Qadir hai"
  3,166,jo nuqsaan larai ke din tumhe pouncha woh Allah ke azan se tha aur is liye tha ke Allah dekh le tum mein se momin kon hain
  3,167,"aur munafiq kon, woh munafiq ke jab unn se kaha gaya aao, Allah ki raah mein jung karo ya kam az kam ( apne shehar ki ) mudafat hi karo, to kehnay lagey agar hamein ilm hota ke aaj jung hogi to hum zaroor sath chaltay yeh baat jab woh keh rahay thay uss waqt woh imaan ki nisbat kufar se ziyada qareeb thay woh apni zabanon se woh baatein kehte hain jo un ke dilon mein nahi hoten, aur jo kuch woh dilon mein chupatay hain Allah usay khoob jaanta hai"
  3,168,yeh wohi log hain jo khud to baithy rahay o Raan ke jo bhai band larnay gay aur maaray gay un ke mutaliq unhon ne keh diya ke a giroh hamari baat maan letay to nah maaray jatay un se kaho agar tum apne qoul mein sachey ho to khud tumhari mout jab aeye ussay taall kar dikha dena
  3,169,"jo log Allah ki raah mein qatal hue hain inhen murda nah samjhoo, woh to haqeeqat mein zindah hain, apne rab ke paas rizaq pa rahay hain"
  3,170,"jo kuch Allah ne apne fazl se inhen diya hai uss par khush o Khurram hain, aur mutmaen hain ke jo ahal imaan unkay peechay duniya mein reh gay hain aur abhi wahan nahi puhanche hain un ke liye bhi kisi khauf aur ranj ka mauqa nahi hai"
  3,171,woh Allah ke inaam aur is ke fazl par Shadan o Ferhan hain aur un ko maloom ho chuka hai ke Allah mominoun ke ajar ko zaya nahi karta
  3,172,jin logon ne zakham khanay ke baad bhi Allah aur rasool ki pukaar par labaik kaha unn mein jo ashkhaas nekokaar aur parhaiz gaar hain unn ke liye bara ajar hai
  3,173,"aur woh jin se logon ne kaha ke,"" tumhary khilaaf barri faujein jama hui hain, unn se daro "", to yeh sun kar un ka imaan aur barh gaya aur onhon ne jawab diya ke hamaray liye Allah kaafi hai aur wohi behtareen karsaazay hai"
  3,174,"aakhir-kaar woh Allah taala ki Nemat aur fazl ke sath palat aeye, un ko kisi qisam ka zarrar bhi nah pouncha aur Allah ki Raza par chalne ka Sharf bhi inhen haasil ho gaya, Allah bara fazl frmane wala hai"
  3,175,"ab tumhe maloom ho gaya ke woh darasal shetan tha jo apne doston se khuwa makhuwa dara raha tha lehaza aindah tum insanon se nah darna, mujh se darna agar tum haqeeqat mein sahib imaan ho"
  3,176,"(ae Peghamber Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam) jo log aaj kufar ki raah mein barri daud dhoop kar rahay hain un ki sargarmia tumhe aazurda nah karen, yeh Allah ka kuch bhi nah bigaar saken ge Allah ka iradah yeh hai ke unn ke liye akhirat mein koi hissa nah rakhay, aur bil akhir un ko sakht saza milnay wali hai"
  3,177,"jo log imaan ko chore kar kufar ke khredar banay hain woh yaqeenan Allah ka koi nuqsaan nahi kar rahay hain, unn ke liye dard naak azaab tayyar hai"
  3,178,"yeh dheel jo hum inhen diye jatay hain is ko yeh kafir apne haq mein behtari nah samjhain, hum to inhen is liye dheel day rahay hain ke yeh khoob baar gunah samaitt len, phir unn ke liye sakht zaleel karne wali saza hai"
  3,179,Allah mominoun ko is haalat mein hargiz nah rehne day ga jis mein tum is waqt paye jatay ho woh pak logon ko napak logon se allag kar ke rahay ga magar Allah ka yeh tareeqa nahi hai ke tum ko ghaib par mutala kar day ghaib ki baatein bitanay ke liye to woh apne Rasolo-n mein jis ko chahta hai muntakhib kar laita hai lehaza ( umoor ghaib ke baray mein ) Allah aur is ke rasool par imaan rakho agar tum imaan aur khuda tarsi ki rawish par chalo ge to tum ko bara ajar miley ga
  3,180,"jin logon ko Allah ne apne fazl se nawaza hai aur phir woh bukhal se kaam letay hain woh is khayaal mein nah rahen ke yeh bkhili un ke liye achi hai nahi, yeh un ke haq mein nihayat buri hai jo kuch woh apni kanjoosi se jama kar rahay hain wohi qayamat ke roz un ke gilaay ka taoq ban jaye ga zameen aur asmano ki meeras Allah hi ke liye hai aur tum jo kuch karte ho Allah is se bakhabar hai"
  3,181,"Allah ne unn logon ka qoul suna jo kehte hain ke Allah faqeer hai aur hum ghanni hain un ki yeh baatein bhi hum likh len ge, aur is se pehlay jo woh payghambaroon ko na-haq qatal karte rahay hain woh bhi un ke nama aamaal mein Sabt hai ( jab faisla ka waqt aeye ga uss waqt ) hum un se kahin ge ke lau, ab azaab jahannum ka maza chako"
  3,182,"yeh tumahray apne hathon ki kamaai hai, Allah apne bundon ke liye zalim nahi hai"
  3,183,"jo log kehte hain"" Allah ne hum ko hadaayat kar di hai ke hum kisi ko rasool tasleem nah karen jab taq woh hamaray samnay aisi qurbani nah kere jisay ( ghaib se aakar ) aag kha le "", unn se kaho,"" tumahray paas mujh se pehlay bohat se rasool aa chuke hain jo bohat si roshan nishanain laaye thay aur woh nishani bhi laaye thay jis ka tum zikar karte ho, phir agar ( imaan laane ke liye yeh shart paish karne mein ) tum sachey ho to unn Rasolo-n ko tum ne kyun qatal kya? """
  3,184,ab ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! agar yeh log tumhe jutlatay hain to bohat se rasool tum se pehlayjhutla-ay ja chuke hain jo khuli khuli nishanain aur saheefay aur roshni bakhsnay wali kitaaben laaye thay
  3,185,"aakhir-kaar har shakhs ko marna hai aur tum sab apne apne poooray ajar qayamat ke roz panay walay ho kamyaab darasal woh hai jo wahan aatish dozakh se bach jaye aur jannat mein daakhil kar diya jaye rahi yeh duniya, to yeh mehez aik zahir fraib cheez hai"
  3,186,"mslmano! tumhe maal aur jaan dono ki aazmayshin paish aa kar rahen gi, aur tum ahal kitaab aur mushriqeen se bohat si takleef da baatein suno ge agar un sab halaat mein tum sabr aur khuda tarsi ki rawish par qaim raho to yeh barray hosla ka kaam hai"
  3,187,"inn ahal kitaab ko woh ehad bhi yaad dlao jo Allah ne un se liya tha ke tumhe kitaab ki talemaat ko logon mein phelana hoga, inhen posheeda rakhna nahi hoga magar unhon ne kitaab ko pas pusht daal diya aur thori qeemat par ussay beech dala kitna bura kaarobar hai jo yeh kar rahay hain"
  3,188,tum unn logon ko azaab se mehfooz nah samjhoo jo apne krtoton par khush hain aur chahtay hain ke aisay kamon ki tareef unhen haasil ho jo fi al waqea unhon ne nahi kiye hain haqeeqat mein un ke liye dard naak saza tayyar hai
  3,189,zameen aur aasman ka maalik Allah hai aur is ki qudrat sab par haawi hai
  3,190,zameen aur asmano ki paidaiesh mein aur raat aur din ke baari baari se anay mein unn hosh mand logon ke liye bohat nishanain hain
  3,191,"jo uthte, baithtay aur لlaytay har haal mein khuda ko yaad karte hain aur aasman o zameen ki saakht mein ghhor o fikar karte hain ( woh be ikhtiyar bo l- uthte hain )"" parvar-digaar! yeh sab kuch to ne fuzool aur be maqsad nahi banaya hai, to pak hai is se ke abs kaam kere pas ae rab! hamein dozakh ke azaab se bacha le"
  3,192,"to ne jisay dozakh mein dala usay Dur haqeeqat barri zillat o ruswai mein daal diya, aur phir aisay zaalmon ka koi madad gaar nah hoga"
  3,193,"maalik! hum ne aik pukarnay walay ko suna jo imaan ki taraf bulaataa tha aur kehta tha ke apne rab ko manu hum ne is ki dawat qubool kar li, pas ae hamaray aaqa! jo qasoor hum se hue hain un se dar guzar farma, jo buraiyan hum mein hain inhen daur kar day aur hamara khtama naik logon ke sath kar"
  3,194,"khudawanda! jo waday to ne apne Rasolo-n ke zareya se kiye hain unn ko hamaray sath poora kar aur qayamat ke din hamein ruswai mein nah daal, be shak to apne waday ke khilaaf karne wala nahi hai """
  3,195,"jawab mein un ke rab ne farmaya,"" mein tum mein se kisi ka amal zaya karne wala nahi hon khuwa mard ho ya aurat, tum sab aik dosray ke hum jins ho lehaza jin logon ne meri khatir apne watan chhorey aur jo Meer y raah mein apne gharon se nikalay gay aur sataye gay aur mere liye larray aur maaray gay unn ke sab qasoor mein maaf kar dun ga aur inhen aisay baghoon mein daakhil karoon ga jin ke neechay nhrin behti hon gi yeh unn ki jaza hai Allah ke haan aur behtareen jaza Allah hi ke paas hai """
  3,196,ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam! duniya ke mulkon mein khuda ke nafarman logon kichallat phirat tumhe kisi dhokay mein nah daaley
  3,197,"yeh mehez chand roza zindagi ka thora sa lutaf hai, phir yeh sab jahannum mein jayen ge jo bad tareen jaye qarar hai"
  3,198,"bar aks is ke jo log apne rab se drtay hue zindagi busr karte hain un ke liye aisay baagh hain jin ke neechay nhrin behti hain, un baghoon mein woh hamesha rahen ge, Allah ki taraf se yeh samaan ziyafat hai un ke liye, aur jo kuch Allah ke paas hai naik logon ke liye wohi sab se behtar hai"
  3,199,"ahal kitaab mein bhi kuch log aisay hain jo Allah ko mantay hain, is kitaab par imaan laatay hain jo tumhari taraf bhaije gayi hai aur iss kitaab prbhi imaan rakhtay hain jo is se pehlay khud un ki taraf bhaije gayi thi, Allah ke agay jhuke hue hain, aur Allah ki ayaat ko thori si qeemat par beech nahi dete un ka ajar un ke rab ke paas hai aur Allah hisaab chukane mein der nahi lagaata"
  3,200,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, sabr se kaam lau, baatil paraston ke muqaabla mein pa mardi dikhao, haq ki khidmat ke liye kamar basta raho, aur Allah se drtay raho, umeed hai ke Falah pao ge"
